    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been totally babied, garage-kept, and drives like a dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin, you\u2019re going to love it!",
