    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true time capsule: this vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. The factory paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks or rock chips, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains untouched by time; the premium leather upholstery is supple and completely free of creasing or wear, still carrying that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule with all fluids recently flushed and a comprehensive service history included. This car drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership\u2014tight, responsive, and exceptionally smooth. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a flawless example of automotive excellence.",
